{
  "id": "RAW_1a7b9d",
  "title": "Seed Research | 视频生成模型最新成果，可仅靠视觉认知世界！现已开源",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mXaktIsD3w5BgCJQb6R7xQ",
  "date": "2025-02-10 03:03:43",
  "author": "Seed Research",
  "siteName": "字节跳动Seed",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section>\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"123\" data-backw=\"578\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"123\" data-imgfileid=\"100003135\" data-ratio=\"0.21296296296296297\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e43be5-80eb-4738-4c4a-01bcc8990d00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 100%;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e43be5-80eb-4738-4c4a-01bcc8990d00/public\">\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:10px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n         <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">视频生成实验模型“VideoWorld”由豆包大模型团队与北京交通大学、中国科学技术大学联合提出。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同于 Sora 、DALL-E 、Midjourney 等主流多模态模型，VideoWorld 在业界首次实现无需依赖语言模型，即可认知世界。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n         <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n          <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;font-size: 15px;\">正如李飞飞教授 9 年前 TED 演讲中提到 “幼儿可以不依靠语言理解真实世界”，VideoWorld 仅通过 “视觉信息”，即浏览视频数据，就能让机器掌握推理、规划和决策等复杂能力。团队实验发现，仅 300M 参数量下，VideoWorld 已取得可观的模型表现。</span>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现有模型大多依赖语言或标签数据学习知识，很少涉及纯视觉信号的学习。然而，语言并不能捕捉真实世界中的所有知识。例如，折纸、打领结等复杂任务，难以通过语言清晰表达。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为一种通用视频生成实验模型，VideoWorld 去掉语言模型，实现了统一执行理解和推理任务。同时，它基于</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">一种潜在动态模型，可高效压缩视频帧间的变化信息，显著提升知识学习效率和效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在不依赖任何强化学习搜索或奖励函数机制前提下，<span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">VideoWorld&nbsp;</span>达到了专业 5 段 9x9 围棋水平，并能够在多种环境中，执行机器人任务。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队认为，尽管面向真实世界的视频生成和泛化仍存在很大挑战，视频生成依然可以成为一种通用的知识学习方法，并在现实世界充当思考和行动的“人工大脑”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\"><strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，该项目代码与模型已开源，欢迎体验交流。</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></p>\n  <blockquote class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"192\" data-source-title=\"\">\n   <section class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">VideoWorld: Exploring Knowledge Learning from Unlabeled Videos</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文链接：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.09781</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">代码链接：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://github.com/bytedance/VideoWorld</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">项目主页：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-indent: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://maverickren.github.io/VideoWorld.github.io</span><em><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"></span></em></p>\n   </section>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"></span></em></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;1. 模型仅靠“视觉”即可学习知识&nbsp;</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">面向本次研究，研究团队构建了两个实验环境：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">视频围棋对战和视频机器人模拟操控。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中，围棋可以很好地评估模型的规则学习、推理和规划能力，且围棋关键信息仅有黑白两色及棋盘，可将外观、纹理等复杂细节与高级知识的评估分离，非常适合对上述问题的探索。同时，团队还选取了机器人任务，以考察模型在理解控制规则和规划任务方面的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在模型训练环节，团队构建了一个包含大量视频演示数据的离线数据集，让模型“观看”学习，以此得到一个可以根据过往观测，预测未来画面的视频生成器。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型架构上，团队使用朴素的自回归模型实例化视频生成器，它包含一个 VQ-VAE 编码器 - 解码器和一个自回归 Transformer 。编码器负责将视频帧（画面）转换为离散标记，Transformer 在训练期间使用这些标记预测下一标记。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在推理过程中，Transformer 生成下一帧（画面）的离散标记，这些标记随后由解码器转换回像素空间。通过任务相关的映射函数，模型可将生成画面转换为任务执行动作。这让视频生成实验模型可在不依赖任何动作标签情况下，学习和执行具体任务。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">基于上述朴素的框架对围棋和机器人视频数据进行建模，团队观测到，模型可以掌握基本的围棋规则、走棋策略以及机器人操纵能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但团队同时也发现，视频序列的知识挖掘效率显著落后于文本形式，具体如下图所示。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"390\" data-cropselx1=\"88\" data-cropselx2=\"303\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"246\" data-height=\"1004\" data-imgfileid=\"100006122\" data-ratio=\"0.6314814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0c411e48-ba03-40e1-f9ef-a2c0558d8f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"876\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0c411e48-ba03-40e1-f9ef-a2c0558d8f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队将这归因于——视频中存在大量冗余信息，影响了模型的学习效率。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，学习棋子移动过程中，模型只需通过状态序列中少量位置标记编码，但面向视频数据，编码器则会产生过多冗余标记，不利于模型对复杂知识的快速学习。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;2. 压缩视觉变化，让视频学习更加高效&nbsp;</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据上述观测结果，团队提出 VideoWorld 。<strong>它在保留丰富视觉信息的同时，压缩了关键决策和动作相关的视觉变化，实现了更有效的视频学习。</strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通常，视频编码需要数百或数千个离散标记来捕捉每帧内的视觉信息，这导致知识被稀疏地嵌入标记中。为此，VideoWorld 引入了一个潜在动态模型（Latent Dynamics Model, LDM），可将帧间视觉变化压缩为紧凑的潜在编码，提高模型的知识挖掘效率。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">举例而言，围棋中的多步棋盘变化或机器人连续动作均表现出强时间相关性，通过将这些多步变化压缩成紧凑嵌入，不仅让策略信息更紧凑，还将前向规划指导信息进行编码。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LDM 采用了 MAGVITv2 风格的编码器 - 解码器结构，同时取消时间维度下采样，以保留每帧细节。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于一个视频片段，LDM 采样每一帧及其后续固定数量帧，编码器先以因果方式提取每帧特征图，且进行量化，以保留详细视觉信息。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">接下来，LDM 定义了一组注意力模块和对应可学习向量。每个向量通过注意力机制捕捉第一帧至后续固定帧的动态变化信息，然后通过 FSQ 量化。其中，量化器作为信息筛选器，防止 LDM 简单记忆后续帧原始内容，而非压缩关键动态信息。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后，解码器使用第一帧的特征图和帧之间的视觉变化编码重建后续帧，最终实现对未来动作的预测和规划，实现对知识的认知学习。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下图为模型架构概览，左侧为整体架构，右侧为潜在动态模型。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"381\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"1345\" data-imgfileid=\"100006125\" data-ratio=\"0.6592592592592592\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/243ed130-9e27-4d46-6391-5aa4753a5400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2040\" height=\"1345\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"2040\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/243ed130-9e27-4d46-6391-5aa4753a5400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过使用多个向量顺序编码第一帧到后续多帧的动态变化，VideoWorld 实现了紧凑且信息丰富的视觉表示，可以捕捉视觉序列中的短期和长期依赖关系。这对于长期推理和规划任务至关重要。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过引入 LDM ，VideoWorld 在仅有 300M 参数量下，达到专业 5 段的 9x9 围棋水平，且不依赖任何强化学习中的搜索或奖励函数机制。在机器人任务上，VideoWorld 也展现出了对多任务、多环境的泛化能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有关 LDM 的更多详细信息，请阅读论文。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;3. 纯视觉模型可“预测”未来，并能“理解”因果关系&nbsp;</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对 LDM 提高视频学习效率的原因，团队进行了更为细致地分析，得出如下 3 点结论：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LDM 建模了训练集的数据模式。</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下图为 LDM 潜在编码 UMAP 可视化呈现，面向围棋和机器人训练集，每个点代表一个潜在编码。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中，UMAP 是一种流行的降维算法，用于将高维数据映射到低维空间，展现模型特征提取情况。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在下图左侧中，奇数步表示白方走棋，偶数步表示黑方，图例展示了新增黑棋的一些常见模式。UMAP 可视化表明：LDM 建模了训练集中常见的走棋模式，并能将短期和长期数据模式压缩至潜在空间中，提取并总结走棋规律。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同理，下图右侧为机械臂沿 X/Y/Z 轴运动方向可视化潜在编码，随着步数（Step）增多，也能看到 LDM 可以建模多步动态依赖关系。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"349\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"1028\" data-imgfileid=\"100006126\" data-ratio=\"0.6037037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cea4722b-4f50-48ed-2814-b98a4950a500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1702\" height=\"1028\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"1702\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cea4722b-4f50-48ed-2814-b98a4950a500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LDM 帮助模型在测试时进行前向规划。</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队还研究了 LDM 在模型推理中的价值。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如下图 UMAP 可视化所示，在测试阶段，模型生成的潜在编码按照时间步（Time-step）进行分组，使得模型能够从更长远视角进行围棋决策。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"281\" data-backw=\"435\" data-cropselx1=\"97\" data-cropselx2=\"338\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"281\" data-height=\"1142\" data-imgfileid=\"100006123\" data-ratio=\"0.6453703703703704\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f126cba0-e630-454e-52fe-9a391a218200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"980\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f126cba0-e630-454e-52fe-9a391a218200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在机器人场景实验中，团队也观察到了类似现象。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下图展示了 VideoWorld 在不同机器人操控任务中预测的潜在编码。不同时间步的潜在编码根据任务类型进行分组，突显了模型逐步捕捉特定任务长程变化的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"532\" data-backw=\"557\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/IrH3BAPESuh0OrV2TkQvZnZyXl8zA63ibatiaXDD4rZZgE4QoWkOcic8yJcL3tbYnLO1buJ3h7I7bOurFOCAdYpXQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"44.15094339622642\" data-cropx2=\"990\" data-cropy1=\"0\" data-cropy2=\"903.3962264150944\" data-height=\"1421\" data-imgfileid=\"100006124\" data-ratio=\"0.9545454545454546\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f1118e7-2164-4b21-02e0-e46e17f09e00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"946\" data-width=\"836\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f1118e7-2164-4b21-02e0-e46e17f09e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LDM 可以生成因果相关的编码。&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为进一步研究潜在编码的影响，团队进行了一项干预实验：用随机标记替换不同时间步的潜在编码，并观察其对模型性能的影响。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验结果显示，干预第一个编码的影响最大，这可能由于编码之间存在因果依赖，团队认为：改变第一个编码，即下一时间步的最佳决策，会影响所有未来的决策，侧面说明模型可生成因果相关编码，理解因果关系。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(89, 160, 250);-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;\">&nbsp;4. 写在最后&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管 VideoWorld 在围棋和模拟机器人操控环境中展现了卓越性能，团队同时也意识到，其在真实世界环境中的应用，仍面临着高质量视频生成和多环境泛化等挑战。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在未来，团队将着力解决这些难题，推动视频生成模型成为真实世界中的通用知识学习器。</span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "豆包团队发布 VideoWorld，一种通过视觉信息学习，应用于围棋和机器人控制的视频生成模型，实现了无需语言模型即可认知世界。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "豆包团队发布 VideoWorld，一种通过视觉信息学习，应用于围棋和机器人控制的视频生成模型，实现了无需语言模型即可认知世界。",
  "summary": "VideoWorld 是由豆包大模型团队联合北京交通大学、中国科学技术大学提出的视频生成模型。该模型创新之处在于，它解决了现有模型对语言的依赖性及其带来的局限性，无需依赖语言模型，仅通过观看视频数据就能学习和理解世界，进行推理、规划和决策。VideoWorld 使用潜在动态模型 (LDM) 压缩视频帧间的变化信息，提高知识学习效率。LDM 通过注意力机制和量化器，保留关键视觉信息。实验表明，该模型在围棋和机器人任务中表现出色，在仅有 300M 参数量下，达到专业 5 段的 9x9 围棋水平。该项目代码与模型已开源。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "VideoWorld 实现了仅通过视觉信息进行知识学习的突破。",
      "explanation": "该模型不依赖语言模型，通过观看视频数据，学习推理、规划和决策等复杂能力，模拟了人类幼儿不依靠语言理解世界的方式，是知识学习上的一次突破。"
    },
    {
      "point": "潜在动态模型（LDM）提升视频学习效率。",
      "explanation": "LDM 压缩了关键决策和动作相关的视觉变化，在保留丰富视觉信息的同时，实现了更有效的视频学习。"
    },
    {
      "point": "VideoWorld 展现出预测未来和理解因果关系的能力。",
      "explanation": "通过干预实验，证明模型可以生成因果相关的编码，理解因果关系，从而更好地进行预测和规划。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LDM 帮助模型在测试时进行前向规划。",
      "explanation": "在测试阶段，模型生成的潜在编码按照时间步进行分组，使得模型能够从更长远视角进行围棋决策，体现了 LDM 的实际应用价值。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "VideoWorld 在业界首次实现无需依赖语言模型，即可认知世界。",
    "视频生成依然可以成为一种通用的知识学习方法，并在现实世界充当思考和行动的“人工大脑”。",
    "LDM 建模了训练集中常见的走棋模式，并能将短期和长期数据模式压缩至潜在空间中，提取并总结走棋规律。"
  ],
